 with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"role":"collection","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshot":{"title":"MLNMapSnapshot","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshot","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshot","abstract":[{"text":"An image generated by a snapshotter object.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapSnapshot"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotter":{"title":"MLNMapSnapshotter","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","isActive":true},{"text":" generates static raster images of the map. Each snapshot","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"image depicts a portion of a map defined by an ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotOptions"},{"text":" object","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"you provide. The snapshotter generates an ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshot"},{"text":" object","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"asynchronously, calling ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" methods if defined, then"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"passing it into a completion handler once tiles and other resources needed for","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the snapshot are finished loading.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapSnapshotter","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotterdelegate","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Optional methods about significant events when creating a snapshot using an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","type":"reference"},{"text":" object.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","title":"MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPointCollection":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpointcollection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"disconnected vertices, specified as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"type":"text","text":" instances. The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"points in the collection may be related but are not connected spatially. For"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"example, you could use a point collection to represent all the trees in an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"orchard.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNPointCollection","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNPointCollection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"title":"MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolyline":{"title":"MLNPolyline","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolyline","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of two or more vertices,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"specified as "},{"code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" instances, and the line segments that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connect them. For example, you could use an polyline to represent a road or the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"path along which something moves."}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNPolyline","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotter/addAnnotation:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter\/addAnnotation:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter\/addannotation:","abstract":[{"text":"Adds an annotation to the snapshotter.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"addAnnotation:"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolyline":{"title":"MLNMultiPolyline","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolyline","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"polylines. For example, you could use a multipolyline shape to represent both"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sides of a divided highway (dual carriageway), excluding the median (central"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reservation): each carriageway would be a distinct "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object."}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNMultiPolyline","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol"}}}